        ### Installation
        ```bash
        $ [sudo] pip install pid-trap
        ```
        
        ```bash
        $ [sudo] npm i -g pid-trap
        ```
        
        #### Examples
        ```bash
        sleep 5 &
        pid-trap $! echo beep
        ```
        
